  "claim_short": "Let T be a bounded linear operator on a Banach space X. If T has dense small periodic sets and every operator I - T^n, n >= 1, has closed range, then the periodic points of T are dense in X. In particular, under the same closed-range hypothesis, a hypercyclic operator with dense small periodic sets is chaotic.",
